        {
          "class": "DepictionMarkdownView",
          "markdown": "**AntiDarkSword** defends jailbroken devices against WebKit RCE exploits and iMessage zero-click attack chains — including **Coruna**, **DarkSword**, and **BLASTPASS** — at the injection layer before any payload reaches the app.",
          "useRawFormat": false
        },
        {
          "class": "DepictionSpacerView",
          "spacing": 8
        },
        {
          "class": "DepictionSeparatorView"
        },
        {
          "class": "DepictionSubheaderView",
          "title": "Protection Layers",
          "useBoldText": true
        },
        {
          "class": "DepictionMarkdownView",
          "markdown": "• **WebKit hardening** — hooks WKWebView, WKWebViewConfiguration, WKPreferences, and WKWebpagePreferences to cut renderer-level attack surface\n\n• **iMessage zero-click blocking** — suppresses IMFileTransfer downloads and risky attachment preview generation (HEIC, HEIF, WebP, PDF)\n\n• **Remote content rules** — WKContentRuleList compiled per-process; default-on for messaging and mail apps\n\n• **User Agent spoofing** — overrides `navigator.userAgent` / `userAgentData` via WKUserScript; presets from iOS 15 → macOS, Android, Windows\n\n• **App extension coverage** — Share, NSE, notification content, and iMessage extensions inherit or override their parent app's rules\n\n• **Corellium VM decoy** — fabricates a plausible stat for `/usr/libexec/corelliumd`, spoofs `kern.osversion`, and neutralises env/path probes\n\n• **Daemon protection** — hooks `imagent`, `identityservicesd`, `apsd`, and `IMDPersistenceAgent` at Level 3\n\n• **TrollFools variant** — substrate-free build; injected per-app, no jailbreak required",
          "useRawFormat": false
        },
        {
          "class": "DepictionSeparatorView"
        },
        {
          "class": "DepictionSubheaderView",
          "title": "Auto-Protect Levels",
          "useBoldText": true
        },
        {
          "class": "DepictionMarkdownView",
          "markdown": "• **Level 1** — browsers, mail, messaging, WebKit-heavy apps\n\n• **Level 2** — Level 1 + social and media apps\n\n• **Level 3** — Level 2 + system daemons (iMessage services)\n\nCustom per-app and per-extension rules override the active level for any bundle ID.",
          "useRawFormat": false
        },
        {
          "class": "DepictionSeparatorView"
        },
        {
          "class": "DepictionSubheaderView",
          "title": "Compatibility",
          "useBoldText": true
        },
        {
          "class": "DepictionMarkdownView",
          "markdown": "**iOS 13 – 17**\n\n• `iphoneos-arm64` rootless — Dopamine 2, RootHide, palera1n rootless\n\n• `iphoneos-arm` rootful — palera1n rootful\n\n• `iphoneos-arm` legacy — Checkra1n, unc0ver, Electra (iOS 13–14)\n\n• TrollFools dylib — no jailbreak required (iOS 15+)",
          "useRawFormat": false
        },
